This is a "simple" esp8266 watch using NTP for dates.

It requires a batch of suplemental libraries that I'll eventually replace.

I've tested it on a LinkNode D1
(http://linksprite.com/wiki/index.php5?title=LinkNode_D1)

I'll put a schematic up once everything is finished.

